{"tid":346871,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"香港有無地方有人工蟻巢買","createTime":"2017-08-04T10:13:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-10T15:15:06.000Z","uid":6366,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dea35b3f92732760d46d3b4d554b7f22ddc926fd","tid":346871,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T10:13:39.000Z","msg":"之前一直都想養蟻<br />\n但係係香港都只係見到藍色果啲螞蟻工房<br />\n<br />\n睇好多文章都係講用呢種養螞蟻螞蟻好快死<br />\n而且唔係真係築巢，只係搵路走<br />\n<br />\nGoogle都台灣螞蟻帝國果種人工蟻巢真係可以用黎長養<br />\n但搵唔到香港邊到有<br />\n<br />\n另外想問下有咩品種推介<br />\n同埋走甩唔會影響香港生態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a28d3529b7a91b3bfd0e41e72074e201ace9429b","tid":346871,"uid":72994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T10:33:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/AntsCanada\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fuser%2FAntsCanada&d=YuSwjyxktyc1RY4LuWNYjHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=e3a2f30c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/user/AntsCanada</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個人養蟻，仲有賣下setup"},{"pid":"64edd67a00734576573652f2a0f83d70b80b3fdf","tid":346871,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T10:47:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/AntsCanada\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fuser%2FAntsCanada&d=YuSwjyxktyc1RY4LuWNYjHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=e3a2f30c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/user/AntsCanada</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個人養蟻，仲有賣下setup</blockquote><br />\n一入去見到培養緊紅火蟻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之前高登好似好多人養蟻<br />\n其實香港係咪無得買,一定要係美洲寄過黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c2c16cc067e321ce73b73d2889c14056a30e724","tid":346871,"uid":86893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T11:54:21.000Z","msg":"次次有人提親養蟻都搞到我諗起youtube個段恐怖片<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4bf70f060a25541de2f790a26c96ec4bd832716","tid":346871,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T13:17:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>次次有人提親養蟻都搞到我諗起youtube個段恐怖片<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩片"},{"pid":"ee118057d973fc3f8996943a4c7d26f0e669d726","tid":346871,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T13:18:19.000Z","msg":"幾年前好hit<br />\n而家搵得返好小資料"},{"pid":"f49e6ec575b5dba16fb99d1ae144bb0d7fb869c7","tid":346871,"uid":517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T13:22:35.000Z","msg":"以前淘寶有 依家唔知"},{"pid":"9e9269e9bf83f30192f80392f898990e93d3d2ae","tid":346871,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T13:24:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>次次有人提親養蟻都搞到我諗起youtube個段恐怖片<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩片</blockquote><br />\n倒鉛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fcd32e1dbaba38491997decf9ead82df64ce297","tid":346871,"uid":87339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T13:25:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>次次有人提親養蟻都搞到我諗起youtube個段恐怖片<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩片</blockquote><br />\n倒鉛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係鉛， 係鋁<br />\n<br />\n之後洗完好似藝術品咁"},{"pid":"383e44712a627b58cf594c47520ecc0ecc7bc5bb","tid":346871,"uid":42564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T13:44:59.000Z","msg":"養蟻工具可以係大陸/淘寶買，<br />\n都係呀架力膠比較流行，用綿花加水保濕，<br />\n<br />\n蟻有好多種，建議多做功課先買，<br />\n有大/中/細/微型蟻<br />\n<br />\n大型入門有弓背蟻，微型果啲就鋪道蟻，紅火蟻係好型好粗養，不過新手真係唔好搞，一走蟻就死人，真係死人<br />\n<br />\n我以前養過大段時間，同埋大開頭預左狂死，<br />\n因為蟻對濕度同溫書要求都高，甚至乎太光都唔得，要用遮光紙<br />\n<br />\n如果養得好，啲蟻好快就以幾何級數增加...部落會愈黎愈大..當你由1后50工買返黎養到4000工果陣就知道有幾莊觀"},{"pid":"fe588fe46ffb8eba4e64195efba68eb257206388","tid":346871,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T13:58:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>養蟻工具可以係大陸/淘寶買，<br />\n都係呀架力膠比較流行，用綿花加水保濕，<br />\n<br />\n蟻有好多種，建議多做功課先買，<br />\n有大/中/細/微型蟻<br />\n<br />\n大型入門有弓背蟻，微型果啲就鋪道蟻，紅火蟻係好型好粗養，不過新手真係唔好搞，一走蟻就死人，真係死人<br />\n<br />\n我以前養過大段時間，同埋大開頭預左狂死，<br />\n因為蟻對濕度同溫書要求都高，甚至乎太光都唔得，要用遮光紙<br />\n<br />\n如果養得好，啲蟻好快就以幾何級數增加...部落會愈黎愈大..當你由1后50工買返黎養到4000工果陣就知道有幾莊觀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nTHX 巴打<br />\n我都係諗住養弓背蟻<br />\n大大隻 個形狀又好睇<br />\n<br />\n我見人喂佢地食面包蟲,想知香港咩舖頭會賣<br />\n<br />\n防走果D油用晒要補返又一定會返淘寶淘都幾煩<br />\n<br />\n諗住係淘寶 螞蟻牧場買巢,唔鍾意純呀加力,想賣高身立體困D,大細應點揀?"},{"pid":"5a884f46eb54b2a882c0b2988e2df7c5e92f8e52","tid":346871,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T13:58:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>次次有人提親養蟻都搞到我諗起youtube個段恐怖片<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩片</blockquote><br />\n倒鉛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係鉛， 係鋁<br />\n<br />\n之後洗完好似藝術品咁</blockquote><br />\n有睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74cc204afcd7c3e91ed8969e0bbd752fc4e5bd0e","tid":346871,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T16:49:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2547655770ef4769dd8fe1d2a9f0785043427887","tid":346871,"uid":20448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T16:57:03.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打有圖 養緊可以拎出黎睇下"},{"pid":"99b8213a7861f7cc9b85bda87f99067ea84240e8","tid":346871,"uid":35508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T00:26:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/05/082505_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F05%2F082505_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=bd60bab2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n養緊。。成3，4個月先得8工<br />\n有排先入得巢"},{"pid":"0e6f56b55e0aee7e5c3e70242fa5eae234d2562b","tid":346871,"uid":38017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T00:50:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22dba5e0e9702527a6539fca381d578122aadf65","tid":346871,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T02:03:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/05/082505_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F05%2F082505_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=bd60bab2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n養緊。。成3，4個月先得8工<br />\n有排先入得巢</blockquote><br />\n巴打自己繁殖？<br />\n<br />\n我想知點先入得巢？<br />\n如果一后幾工入個住到過千蟻既巢係咪唔好？"},{"pid":"72a0e7282dc4e0f717da5d69ae618ee956338e31","tid":346871,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T02:03:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nThx 巴打"},{"pid":"cf6f74c6ddd18a85347cd5c01471ee41b1d5d6f7","tid":346871,"uid":86893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T04:16:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>次次有人提親養蟻都搞到我諗起youtube個段恐怖片<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩片</blockquote><br />\n倒鉛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係鉛， 係鋁<br />\n<br />\n之後洗完好似藝術品咁</blockquote><br />\n有睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nQueen Ant A-ChaN，仆你地個街，搞到我去揾番依條片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ca4ebad2746ad716f8b8f19e9442f206df2cda0","tid":346871,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T06:00:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>次次有人提親養蟻都搞到我諗起youtube個段恐怖片<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩片</blockquote><br />\n倒鉛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係鉛， 係鋁<br />\n<br />\n之後洗完好似藝術品咁</blockquote><br />\n有睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nQueen Ant A-ChaN，仆你地個街，搞到我去揾番依條片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好好奇<br />\n可唔可以形容下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ad7aeab418b8217a3b5f6b85ac0cea0a2988b4f","tid":346871,"uid":61334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T06:07:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>次次有人提親養蟻都搞到我諗起youtube個段恐怖片<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩片</blockquote><br />\n倒鉛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係鉛， 係鋁<br />\n<br />\n之後洗完好似藝術品咁</blockquote><br />\n有睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nQueen Ant A-ChaN，仆你地個街，搞到我去揾番依條片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好好奇<br />\n可唔可以形容下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nx2"},{"pid":"40bd7ca8d140d3b7b5adb0bfcac1fead1d65d10e","tid":346871,"uid":35508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T07:56:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/05/082505_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F05%2F082505_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=bd60bab2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n養緊。。成3，4個月先得8工<br />\n有排先入得巢</blockquote><br />\n巴打自己繁殖？<br />\n<br />\n我想知點先入得巢？<br />\n如果一后幾工入個住到過千蟻既巢係咪唔0好？</blockquote><br />\n因為之前買左一后幾十工想直接入巢 點知工好易死 到手個陣死哂d工 之後仲唔小心整死埋隻后全滅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n間野另外送左一隻后比我 宜家慢慢培育緊"},{"pid":"9ac8f96c1d9744734a0c90441a119ddcd933aa8b","tid":346871,"uid":86893,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T07:57:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>次次有人提親養蟻都搞到我諗起youtube個段恐怖片<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩片</blockquote><br />\n倒鉛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係鉛， 係鋁<br />\n<br />\n之後洗完好似藝術品咁</blockquote><br />\n有睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nQueen Ant A-ChaN，仆你地個街，搞到我去揾番依條片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好好奇<br />\n可唔可以形容下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nx2</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一開始3集內容好簡單，你睇住人工蟻巢養蟻D蟻由少變多，仲要搞到個氣氛好開心好似睇兒童節目咁，當中有少量恐怖野<br />\n<br />\n去到第4集一下大爆發，講有種蟲（好似係寄生蟲？）一下食曬殺曬D蟻，但最恐怖係佢用大量道具+effect+音樂+拍攝手法，成段片詭異到無得形容，我未見過有任何野係同依段片相似<br />\n<br />\n之後D集數我完全禁落去都唔敢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47d6589d3d9a589fe735fd6a88834c9fd8a46ba3","tid":346871,"uid":35508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T07:59:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/05/082505_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F05%2F082505_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=bd60bab2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n養緊。。成3，4個月先得8工<br />\n有排先入得巢</blockquote><br />\n巴打自己繁殖？<br />\n<br />\n我想知點先入得巢？<br />\n如果一后幾工入個住到過千蟻既巢係咪唔0好？</blockquote><br />\n因為之前買左一后幾十工想直接入巢 點知工好易死 到手個陣死哂d工 之後仲唔小心整死埋隻后全滅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n間野另外送左一隻后比我 宜家慢慢培育緊</blockquote><br />\n所以宣家養緊係買滿100人仔送既贈品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果得幾工入大巢以我所知空間太大 d工蟻會將d垃圾亂咁放 同埋個賣家話用試管有助保育"},{"pid":"3e7761d1e759c401d8878f397edb98728f131783","tid":346871,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T08:06:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/05/082505_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F05%2F082505_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=bd60bab2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n養緊。。成3，4個月先得8工<br />\n有排先入得巢</blockquote><br />\n巴打自己繁殖？<br />\n<br />\n我想知點先入得巢？<br />\n如果一后幾工入個住到過千蟻既巢係咪唔0好？</blockquote><br />\n因為之前買左一后幾十工想直接入巢 點知工好易死 到手個陣死哂d工 之後仲唔小心整死埋隻后全滅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n間野另外送左一隻后比我 宜家慢慢培育緊</blockquote><br />\n所以宣家養緊係買滿100人仔送既贈品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果得幾工入大巢以我所知空間太大 d工蟻會將d垃圾亂咁放 同埋個賣家話用試管有助保育</blockquote><br />\n我頭先問淘寶賣家佢都話太大地方蟻會無安全感<br />\n<br />\n考慮緊油一后十幾工定兩后十幾工<br />\n但係你話工好易食我又驚無晒工兩隻后無人湊<br />\n<br />\n巴打都係淘寶買？運輸過程太長所以死晒？"}]}